<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>

<p>Three <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">column</rs>s, fluted above: i. standing, facing north west; very weathered. ii. standing, facing north west. iii. fragment of a <rs type="objectType">column</rs> shaft.</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>

<p>Each inscribed below fluting; i. at 1.35 above base; ii. at 1.34.</p>
</div><div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p><measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.07</measure></p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0000" notBefore="0000" cert="low">Second century A.D.</date>
(<rs type="criteria">lettering</rs>)</p>
</div>
<div type="edition" lang="grc">
<head lang="en">Edition</head>
